{"tid":1083433,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"港漫畫家奪日漫畫獎　《女漢子騎士也想談戀愛！》獲評繪圖非常有水準","createTime":"2019-03-29T15:18:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T16:13:38.000Z","uid":39464,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c07915abb6b71059e58014803aacb8b463c42df5","tid":1083433,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T15:18:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/comics-01_2eGQs_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fcomics-01_2eGQs_1200x0.png&h=946fc6c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港揚威海外系列，唔好畀佢停！日前日本講談社 Sirius 輕小說編輯部漫畫賞公布得獎名單，香港漫畫家 K9ehvvf 憑作品《女漢子騎士也想談戀愛！》獲得〈草圖分鏡部門〉特別獎，贏得 20 萬日圓（約港幣 1 萬 4 千元）獎金，並獲「安排責任編輯」，有機會在日本出道。<br />\n<br />\n講談社為日本知名出版社，旗下刊物包括《週刊少年 Magazine》、《別冊少年 Magazine》等。k9ehvvf 這次憑《女漢子騎士也想談戀愛！》贏得講談社主辦的漫畫比賽中〈草圖分鏡部門〉特別獎，是針對草圖、分鏡設計與作畫技術的獎項。講談社 Sirius 編輯部稱讚 k9ehvvf 的作品「繪圖功力非常地具有水準。充滿動力的構圖，畫面的空間呈現也相當值得讚許。」同時給出建議指「我想作家對於日本漫畫相當有著墨，只不過角色人物給予人一點點僵硬的感覺。若能夠對於圖樣及設計多加研究並加以搭配的話，能夠更加精進作品本身。」<br />\n<br />\nK9ehvvf 也有在其 FB 專頁分享得獎消息，並表示：「這不是我第一次得獎，但絕對是目前為止最大的一次。」他事後接受媒體訪問時透露，這次參賽是因為自己從小看日本漫畫長大，「所以很嚮往能參與其中，即使是比賽」。畫了漫畫八、九年的他又提到香港的創作環境其實並不理想，「因為容不下新人」。他解釋：「現代娛樂太多，加上香港人口基數少，只談漫畫創作的話買單的人不會多，很難賺錢，出版社賺不到，新人漫畫創作什麼的根本不想。」<br />\n<br />\n這次獲獎作品《女漢子騎士也想談戀愛！》部分草圖分鏡可在此鑑賞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://medibang.com/book/3w1901161646185590008312376/view/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedibang.com%2Fbook%2F3w1901161646185590008312376%2Fview%2F&d=tn6C2tKLXSv13zRFu6un7Z1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=d394a5e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medibang.com/book/3w1901161646185590008312376/view/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/culture/%E6%B8%AF%E6%BC%AB%E7%95%AB%E5%AE%B6%E5%A5%AA%E6%97%A5%E6%BC%AB%E7%95%AB%E7%8D%8E-%E5%A5%B3%E6%BC%A2%E5%AD%90%E9%A8%8E%E5%A3%AB%E4%B9%9F%E6%83%B3%E8%AB%87%E6%88%80%E6%84%9B-%E7%8D%B2%E8%A9%95%E7%B9%AA%E5%9C%96%E9%9D%9E%E5%B8%B8%E6%9C%89%E6%B0%B4%E6%BA%96/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25BC%25AB%25E7%2595%25AB%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25A5%25AA%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%25BC%25AB%25E7%2595%25AB%25E7%258D%258E-%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E5%25AD%2590%25E9%25A8%258E%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E4%25B9%259F%25E6%2583%25B3%25E8%25AB%2587%25E6%2588%2580%25E6%2584%259B-%25E7%258D%25B2%25E8%25A9%2595%25E7%25B9%25AA%25E5%259C%2596%25E9%259D%259E%25E5%25B8%25B8%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E6%25BA%2596%2F&d=tn6C2tKLXSv13zRFu6un7Z1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=5ea64c34\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25BC%25AB%25E7%2595%25AB%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25A5%25AA%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%25BC%25AB%25E7%2595%25AB%25E7%258D%258E-%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E5%25AD%2590%25E9%25A8%258E%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E4%25B9%259F%25E6%2583%25B3%25E8%25AB%2587%25E6%2588%2580%25E6%2584%259B-%25E7%258D%25B2%25E8%25A9%2595%25E7%25B9%25AA%25E5%259C%2596%25E9%259D%259E%25E5%25B8%25B8%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E6%25BA%2596%2F&h=8b036bb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/culture/%E6%B8%AF%E6%BC%AB%E7%95%AB%E5%AE%B6%E5%A5%AA%E6%97%A5%E6%BC%AB%E7%95%AB%E7%8D%8E-%E5%A5%B3%E6%BC%A2%E5%AD%90%E9%A8%8E%E5%A3%AB%E4%B9%9F%E6%83%B3%E8%AB%87%E6%88%80%E6%84%9B-%E7%8D%B2%E8%A9%95%E7%B9%AA%E5%9C%96%E9%9D%9E%E5%B8%B8%E6%9C%89%E6%B0%B4%E6%BA%96/</a>"},{"pid":"b664c9c362d94c53fdafcf75d1ce0cb9c842ba68","tid":1083433,"uid":150609,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T15:25:41.000Z","msg":"畫得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好過之前吹奏果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd6c14e81811d58bc69368bba32e748211e9ed5","tid":1083433,"uid":234695,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T15:27:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9D2WSiy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"htt